The package can be installed by any of the following three approaches: 1) Install from the PyPI pip install pystoned 2) Install from the GitHub repository pip install -U git+https://github.com/ds2010/pyStoNED SFA codes and packages for MATLAB ,GAMS, and other high-level mathematical computing languages (e.g., Kalvelagen, 2002; Ji and Lee, 2010; Belotti, Daidone, Ilardi, and Atella, 2013; Álvarez, Barbero, and Zofío, 2020).
